    <p> 
      “Many people have an impression that my hair can’t be touched and I am very girly person who doesn’t like to change (my appearance). But actually, I do have a rough-and-tumble side and can be very boyish at times. Perhaps it’s because of my petite size, people naturally find me more suitable to act in feminine roles,” said the MediaCorp actress, Jeanette Aw who recently showed up with a punky haircut for her upcoming Ch8 blockbuster drama, World at Your Feet..
    </p>

