    <p>
      The bubbly and candid actress shocked the production during an imaging session for the drama recently. Playing the female lead, Mo Yuqing, a toy-boyish soccer fan who falls in love with Wu Weixiong (played by Elvin Ng), Jeanette felt that shaving the sides of her head would help to portray a masculine side of her character.
    </p>
    {{> molecules-figure-with-caption(landscape: true) }}
    <p>
      During her interview with xinmsn, Jeanette revealed that it was her initiative to take this 180-degree transformation. Being well-known for her demure image in hit dramas like The Little Nyonya and The Dream Makers, Jeanette told us that she is open to trying different styles.
    </p>

    <div class="split-insert" data-split-index="0"></div>

    <blockquote>
      "I actually thought about this idea when I was discussing my role with the production team months ago and they actually liked it!"
